<p class=3D"g-md-p">This BFS implementation shows how to initialize a queue=
, track visited nodes using a list or set, and iterate through each node=E2=
=80=99s neighbors, allowing us to traverse a graph efficiently and find sho=
rtest paths in unweighted graphs. </p>
